complexType.Definition: A number of monetary units specified in a currency where the unit of the currency is explicit or implied.

attribute.Name: Amount. Currency. Identifier
attribute.Definition: The currency of the amount.

attribute.Name: Amount Currency. Code List Version. Identifier
attribute.Definition: The VersionID of the UN/ECE Rec9 code list.

complexType.Definition: A set of finite-length sequences of binary octets.

attribute.Name: Binary Object. Format. Text
attribute.Definition: The format of the binary content.

attribute.Name: Binary Object. Mime. Code
attribute.Definition: The mime type of the binary object.

attribute.Name: Binary Object. Encoding. Code
attribute.Definition: Specifies the decoding algorithm of the binary object.

attribute.Name: Binary Object. Character Set. Code
attribute.Definition: The character set of the binary object if the mime type is text.

attribute.Name: Binary Object. Uniform Resource. Identifier
attribute.Definition: The Uniform Resource Identifier that identifies where the binary object is located.

attribute.Name: Binary Object. File. Name
attribute.Definition: The filename of the binary object.

complexType.Definition: A character string (letters, figures, or symbols) that for brevity and/or languange independence may be used to represent or replace a definitive value or text of an attribute together with relevant supplementary information.
complexType.UsageRule: Should not be used if the character string identifies an instance of an object class or an object in the real world, in which case the Identifier. Type should be used.

attribute.Name: Code List. Identifier
attribute.Definition: The identification of a list of codes.

attribute.Name: Code List. Agency. Identifier
attribute.Definition: An agency that maintains one or more lists of codes.

attribute.Name: Code List. Agency Name. Text
attribute.Definition: The name of the agency that maintains the list of codes.

attribute.Name: Code List. Name. Text
attribute.Definition: The name of a list of codes.

attribute.Name: Code List. Version. Identifier
attribute.Definition: The version of the list of codes.

attribute.Name: Code. Name. Text
attribute.Definition: The textual equivalent of the code content component.

attribute.Name: Language. Identifier
attribute.Definition: The identifier of the language used in the code name.

attribute.Name: Code List. Uniform Resource. Identifier
attribute.Definition: The Uniform Resource Identifier that identifies where the code list is located.

attribute.Name: Code List Scheme. Uniform Resource. Identifier
attribute.Definition: The Uniform Resource Identifier that identifies where the code list scheme is located.

complexType.Definition: A particular point in the progression of time together with the relevant supplementary information.

attribute.Name: Date Time. Format. Text
attribute.Definition: The format of the date time content

complexType.Definition: A character string to identify and distinguish uniquely, one instance of an object in an identification scheme from all other objects in the same scheme together with relevant supplementary information.

attribute.Name: Identification Scheme. Identifier
attribute.Definition: The identification of the identification scheme.

attribute.Name: Identification Scheme. Name. Text
attribute.Definition: The name of the identification scheme.

attribute.Name: Identification Scheme. Agency. Identifier
attribute.Definition: The identification of the agency that maintains the identification scheme.

attribute.Name: Identification Scheme. Agency Name. Text
attribute.Definition: The name of the agency that maintains the identification scheme.

attribute.Name: Identification Scheme. Version. Identifier
attribute.Definition: The version of the identification scheme.

attribute.Name: Identification Scheme Data. Uniform Resource. Identifier
attribute.Definition: The Uniform Resource Identifier that identifies where the identification scheme data is located.

attribute.Name: Identification Scheme. Uniform Resource. Identifier
attribute.Definition: The Uniform Resource Identifier that identifies where the identification scheme is located.

complexType.Definition: A list of two mutually exclusive Boolean values that express the only possible states of a Property.

attribute.Name: Indicator. Format. Text
attribute.Definition: Whether the indicator is numeric, textual or binary.

complexType.Definition: A numeric value determined by measuring an object along with the specified unit of measure.

attribute.Name: Measure. Unit. Code
attribute.Definition: The type of unit of measure.

attribute.Name: Measure Unit. Code List Version. Identifier
attribute.Definition: The version of the measure unit code list.

complexType.Definition: Numeric information that is assigned or is determined by calculation, counting, or sequencing. It does not require a unit of quantity or unit of measure.

attribute.Name: Numeric. Format. Text
attribute.Definition: Whether the number is an integer, decimal, real number or percentage.

complexType.Definition: A counted number of non-monetary units possibly including fractions.

attribute.Name: Quantity. Unit. Code
attribute.Definition: The unit of the quantity

attribute.Name: Quantity Unit. Code List. Identifier
attribute.Definition: The quantity unit code list.

attribute.Name: Quantity Unit. Code List Agency. Identifier
attribute.Definition: The identification of the agency that maintains the quantity unit code list

attribute.Name: Quantity Unit. Code List Agency. Name
attribute.Definition: The name of the agency which maintains the quantity unit code list.

complexType.Definition: A character string (i.e. a finite set of characters) generally in the form of words of a language.

attribute.Name: Language. Identifier
attribute.Definition: The identifier of the language used in the content component.

attribute.Name: Language Locale. Identifier
attribute.Definition: The identification of the locale of the language.
